{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, children can recognize and use many forms of conversation and cooperation [75,76].",
    "However, LLM shows some limitations and problems in its use, including ethics and injustice.",
    "In some cases, the scale and complexity of the LLM may create problems in understanding and evaluating the information contained, thus reducing its usefulness [67,77].",
    "Despite these difficulties, the LLM has become essential in artificial intelligence.",
    "These developments can change our understanding of language and how we interact with others."
  ]
}